3" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p><span class="txt2"><small>STEP 4:&nbsp;</small></span><br /><strong><span class="txt2">USE</span></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p class="txt1">USE, INDULGE, LOOK AMAZING AT A FRACTION OF A PRICE, SHOW THE WORLD HOW TERRIFIC YOU FEEL!</p>\r\n<p class="txt1">You LIKE the bag so much and WANT it for LONGER?GREAT!<br />Contact us &ndash; if it is available we can EXTEND the rental period!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid">\r\n<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-3">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p><img alt="55" src="{{media url="wysiwyg/step-3.jpg"}}" height="82" width="84" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p><span class="txt2"><small>STEP 5:&nbsp;</small></span><br /><strong><span class="txt2">RETURN</span></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p class="txt1">Return shipping is FREE and easy.</p>\r\n<p class="txt1">Once your rental period is finished simply pack the bag into the box it came in and use the return self addressed label provided. We book a courier.</p>\r\n<p class="txt1">You are now ready to RENT ANOTHER BAG.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a class="button" href="{{store direct_url="rent.html"}}">GET STARTED</a>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2016-04-05 14:21:41', '2016-04-05 16:42:18', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(14, 'REWARDS AND LOYALTY POINTS', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'rewards-and-loyalty-points', NULL, '<header class="entry-header">\r\n<h1 class="entry-title" style="text-align: center;">REWARDS AND LOYALTY POINTS</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid">\r\n<div class="row-container">\r\n<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: large;"><strong>SPEND&nbsp; &nbsp; EARN&nbsp; &nbsp; REDEEM</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid">\r\n<div class="row-container">\r\n<div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">JOIN RENT-A-BAG AND GET REWARDED EVERY TIME YOU RENT A BAG FROM US OR PURCHASE A BUY-TO-RENT BAG</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Make every pound you spend with us count, at every level.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #fb1c5b;">For every &pound;1 spent you earn 1 POINT</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #fb1c5b;">100 POINTS = &pound;10</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">in RENT-A-BAG credit to redeem against your next rental or purchase.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">ALL PURCHASES EARN POINTS based on the total amount spent.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">EANING POINTS IS EASY:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span style="color: #fb1c5b;"><strong>200 POINTS</strong></span>&nbsp;(=<span style="color: #fb1c5b;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><span><span style="color: #fb1c5b;"><strong>&pound;20</strong></span>&nbsp;</span></span><span>RENT-A-BAG credit</span><span>)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">FOR SINGING UP and creating MY ACCOUNT</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">+</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span style="color: #fb1c5b;"><strong>100 POINTS</strong></span>&nbsp;(=&nbsp;<span><strong><span style="color: #fb1c5b;">&pound;10</span></strong>&nbsp;</span></span><span>RENT-A-BAG credit</span><span>)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">TO REFER A FRIEND AND THE REFERRED FRIEND MAKES A PURCHASE</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">+</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="color: #fb1c5b;">100 POINTS</span></strong>&nbsp;(=&nbsp;<span><strong><span style="color: #fb1c5b;">&pound;10</span></strong>&nbsp;</span></span><span>RENT-A-BAG credit</span><span>)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">REFERRED FRIEND MAKES A REPEAT PURCHASE</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">+</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="color: #fb1c5b;">50 POINTS</span></strong>&nbsp;(=&nbsp;<strong><span style="color: #fb1c5b;">&pound;5</span></strong>&nbsp;RENT-A-BAG credit)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">EARLY RENTAL RETURN</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2016-04-13 06:45:08', '2016-04-13 07:02:03', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

